posting_body: ['Property Address', '658 Grand Ave - D(R) | St. Paul, MN 55105', 'Available:', '08/09/2022', 'Offered By', 'At Home Apartments |', 'show contact info', 'Description', 'Historic Two Bedroom in Prime Location', 'This second floor apartment has a renovated kitchen with new cabinets, granite countertops and stainless steel appliances.', ' You will love the restored hardwood floors, great views, and close proximity to restaurants and shopping.', 'Living at the Tavern Apartments also offers you a convenient parking space located behind the building.', 'Enjoy this prime location on Grand Avenue.', 'Find yourself living in a beautiful apartment above the Tavern on Grand in the best area the city has to offer.', 'The perfect mix of character and convenience are at your doorstep when you are living on Grand Avenue!', 'Residents have included access to the clubhouse and fitness center just over one mile away!', 'Unlimited, coinless laundry on-site for a flat monthly fee.', 'Ask us about our off-street parking availability.', 'Call us at', 'show contact info', 'or visit us at <URL> for more information and tour options.', 'Photos are a representation of the property and may not be of the exact apartment.', 'Amenities', 'Access to Clubhouse and Fitness Center', 'Coinless Laundry On-Site', '*24 hour Emergency Maintenance', 'Convenient Coinless Laundry', 'Hardwood Floors', 'Water & Trash Paid', 'Walk-In Closets', 'Online Rent Payment Portal', 'Details', 'Beds/Baths: 2BD/1.0BA', 'Square Feet: 800', 'Rental Terms', 'Rent: $1,292.00', 'Available:', '08/09/2022', 'Application Fee: $55.00', 'Security Deposit: $600.00', 'Pet Policy', 'Cats allowed', 'Dogs not allowed']
